README
------

These resources are quite helpful to write shell scripts effectively:

* Shell-Programmierung. Das umfassende Handbuch
  Jürgen Wolff
  Galileo Computing, ISBN 3-89842-683-1

* Shell Scripting Recipes. A Problem-Solution Approach
  By Chris Johnson
  http://www.apress.com/9781590594711

* shUnit2 - Bash Testing
  By Michael Wright
  http://www.mikewright.me/blog/2013/10/31/shunit2-bash-testing/

* Defensive BASH Programming
  By Kfir Lavi
  http://www.kfirlavi.com/blog/2012/11/14/defensive-bash-programming/

* A Unix/Linux “find” Command Tutorial
  By Wayne Pollock
  http://content.hccfl.edu/pollock/Unix/FindCmd.htm

Thanks to Gerold Rupprecht and Axel Beckert for their kind advice, and
helpful comments.
